metadata.name: Shinnosuke Nohara
metadata.description: Introducing Shinnosuke, The protagonist of our game!Who lives in thebright & joyous town of Kasukabe in Saitama, along with his friends: Bo, Nene, Masao, Toru & Shiro. This NFT is required to be able to play as Shinnosuke in the upcoming ShinoRevenge P2E game.
